adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Link's Pocket...^$3Spirit Temple...^$4Dodongo's Cavern...^$5Fire Temple...^$6Water Temple...^$7Deku Tree...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...
